test_presence_of_duplicates_in_result:
assert (4 == 3)
 +  where 4 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x7a81e5526980>([-23])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x7a81e5526980> = [[1, -23], [1, -23, 1], [-23], [-23, 1], [1, -23], [1, -23, 1], ...].count
test_if_sublist_product_equals_number:
assert 23 == -23
 +  where 23 = <built-in function prod>([-1, -23])
 +    where <built-in function prod> = math.prod
